title: Final Critical Habitat for the Colorado pikeminnow (Ptychocheilus lucius)
name: final-critical-habitat-for-the-colorado-pikeminnow-ptychocheilus-luciusa45f3
notes: To provide the user with a general idea of areas where final critical habitat for Colorado pikeminnow (Ptychocheilus lucius) occur based on the description provided in the Federal Register. The geographic extent includes San Juan County, New Mexico ; San Juan, Garfield, Wayne, Emery, Grand, Carbon and Uintah Counties, Utah ; and Moffat, Rio Blanco, Garfield, Mesa and Delta Counties, Colorado.
